Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.64,0:23:58.40,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,In the Thames River,\Ncovered by heavy fog...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.47,0:24:01.67,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a monster that pulls cargo\Nships down deep beneath the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.78,0:24:03.77,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Such rumours are\Nspreading around London.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.85,0:24:06.91,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,One evening, a young man\Ndisappears in the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.38,0:24:12.01,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl believes he's still alive,\Nand Holmes starts to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.65,0:24:17.04,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever find yourself in a mystery,\Nplease come see us at Baker Street.
